title: It Is Finished | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: It Is Finished | Joel Osteen
description:
No stronghold can keep you from the amazing future God has prepared for you. The price for your healing has already been paid. You have everything you need to break free from anything that's trying to hold you back!



Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
